          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1631107561056-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the basa is cooked through, transfer it to a plate – this is your <strong>creamy smoked</strong> <strong>basa</strong></p><p>Pour the milk from the pan into a jug (save the pan for later!) – this is your <strong>spiced milk</strong></p><p>Tip: Keep the studded onion in the milk to allow it to infuse further</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1631107565498-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
