            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> linguine</strong> to a pot of<strong> boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the<strong> </strong>linguine for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the<strong> cooked linguine</strong>, reserving 50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[75ml]</span> of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>reserved starchy pasta water</strong> to the jug with the spiced milk</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
