            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat the reserved pan with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining onion </strong>finely</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>flour </strong>and cook for 1 min further</p>",
      "order": 5,
