    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash the <strong>spinach</strong> then chop it roughly</p><p>Chop the <strong>dill</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Break the<strong> creamy smoked</strong> <strong>basa</strong> into small chunks</p>",
