        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion and flour<strong> </strong>have cooked for 1 min, pour the <strong>spiced milk</strong> into the pan and discard the studded onion half<span class=\"text-danger\">[ves]</span></p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until the spiced milk has thickened</p><p>Once thickened, stir through the <strong>garlic & herb spread</strong>,<strong> </strong>the <strong>creamy smoked</strong> <strong>basa chunks</strong>, <strong>chopped spinach </strong>and<strong> chopped dill</strong></p><p>Cook everything for 2 min further or until the spinach has wilted – this is your <strong>creamy smoked basa & dill</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
